Interface EvaluationPolicy

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
CasePolicy, DescriptorPolicy, EvaluateByWorkitemsPolicy, ExcludeUserPolicy, HistoricalEventPolicy, HistoricalStatesPolicy, ModelPolicy, ModelVersionPolicy, ProcessDefinitionDetailsPolicy, ProcessInstanceDetailsPolicy, RepositoryPolicy, SubFolderPolicy, SubsetPolicy, TimeoutPolicy, UserDetailsPolicy, WorklistLayoutPolicy
public interface EvaluationPolicy
extends Serializable

Interface to be implemented by custom query evaluation policies.

An evaluation policy selects (parts of) the strategy for query evaluation, i.e. which model version to use or what subset to deliver.
